-- Andy Murray Beats David Ferrer to Reach Semifinals at Wimbledon
-- B y   B o b   B e n s c h
-- 2012-07-04T18:37:10Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-04/andy-murray-beats-david-ferrer-to-reach-semifinals-at-wimbledon.html
Andy Murray  beat Spain’s David Ferrer
6-7 (5-7), 7-6 (8-6), 6-4, 7-6 (7-4) to advance to the Wimbledon
semifinals for the fourth straight year.  Britain’s Murray, the fourth seed, will play No. 5 Jo-
Wilfried Tsonga of France for a place in the final at the All
England Club in London.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bob Bensch at 
 bbensch@bloomberg.net  